      "content": "i get that, but i already talked to my doctor about the ambien and they just said to take it if i cant sleep. they didn't really say anything about the melatonin since it's just a supplement. do you think it's actually dangerous or is it just like a standard way to boost the effect? i'm just really tired of being exhausted all day.",
