    "summary": "The user is seeking confirmation on whether combining melatonin with prescribed zolpidem (Ambien) is safe and effective for treating insomnia. The assistant repeatedly provides caveats, advises the user to consult their doctor, and avoids giving definitive permission to mix the two substances or increase dosages.",
